## What Makes This Publishable & Novel

| Differentiator | Why It's Unique |
|---|---|
| **Temporally continuous** | Not random snapshots — every 60s for weeks. Enables time-series analysis. |
| **Multi-modal enrichment** | Every frame tagged with weather, taxi density, air quality. No other traffic dataset has this. |
| **Auto-labeled with confidence** | Annotations + confidence scores enable threshold experiments |
| **Failure annotations** | Each frame has a quality/reliability label — enables robustness benchmarking |
| **Drift baselines** | Published baseline drift metrics for the community to benchmark against |
| **Real government data** | ODbL licensed, from a national API — not scraped YouTube |

